(221, 1, '2018-11-22 09:38:55', '2018-11-22 04:08:55', '<em>Mi Amor</em>is Orson Dsouzas debut Konkani music album. Better known as Awesome Orson, he was the winner of Gulf Voice of Mangalore Season 3.<i>Album release date</i>23rd November 2018.\r\n\r\n<strong>Physical copies (CD format) will be available within India at Rs. 150 (with free shipping option).</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Music lovers worldwide can buy downloadable MP3 album at Rs. 250.</strong>\r\n\r\nAlongside Orson, Mi Amor features:\r\nGVOM Season 1 Winner - Vinay John Lewis (Kuwait)\r\nGVOM Season 2 Winner - Gladys Lorena (Kuwait)\r\nGVOM Season 4 Winners - Morvine Quadras (Kuwait) &amp; Joshal Dsouza (UAE)\r\nGVOM Season 5 Winners - Joyline Gonsalves (Kuwait) &amp; Robin Sequeira (UAE)\r\nKonkani Global Award Winner 2013 and 2016 Ms. Shilpa Cutinha\r\n\r\nWith power packed performances from Miss Jacqueline Fernandes, Stephen Cutinha, Meera Crasta, Carol Sequeira &amp; upcoming talented singer Miss Karen Crasta, this album will take the listener on a musical ride!\r\n\r\nMusic composed and arranged by Roshan Dsouza angelore, a maestro and a stalwart of Konkani music, a music director par excellence. Mixed and mastered by Nithin K, Orpheus Studio- Ernakulam. Lyrics are written by Lloyd Rego, Wilson Kateel and Sanjay Borkar. Songs have been recorded at Sandesha Studio (Mangalore), Studio 5 (Mangalore) and AudioKraft Studio, Kuwait.', 'Mi Amor by Orson D''souza', '<em>Mi Amor</em>is Orson Dsouzas debut Konkani music album. Better known as Awesome Orson, he was the winner of Gulf Voice of Mangalore Season 3.<em>Album release date</em>23rd November 2018.\r\n\r\n<strong>Physical copies (CD format) will be available within India at Rs. 150 (with free shipping option).</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Music lovers worldwide can buy downloadable MP3 album at Rs. 250.</strong>\r\n\r\nNote: MP3 format buyers must REGISTER as users during checkout. Downloadable MP3 files will be credited to your Paypassion User Account.', 