(260, 1, '2018-11-21 14:48:11', '2018-11-21 09:18:11', '<em>Mi Amor</em>is Orson Dsouzas debut Konkani music album. Better known as Awesome Orson, he was the winner of Gulf Voice of Mangalore Season 3.<i>Album release date</i>23rd November 2018.\n\n<strong>Physical copies (CD format) will be available within India at Rs. 150 (with free shipping option).</strong>\n\n<strong>Music lovers worldwide can buy downloadable MP3 album at Rs. 250.</strong>\n\nAlongside Orson, Mi Amor features:\nGVOM Season 1 Winner - Vinay John Lewis (Kuwait)\nGVOM Season 2 Winner - Gladys Lorena (Kuwait)\nGVOM Season 4 Winners - Morvine Quadras (Kuwait) &amp; Joshal Dsouza (UAE)\nGVOM Season 5 Winners - Joyline Gonsalves (Kuwait) &amp; Robin Sequeira (UAE)\nKonkani Global Award Winner 2013 and 2016 Ms. Shilpa Cutinha\n\nWith power packed performances from Miss Jacqueline Fernandes, Stephen Cutinha, Meera Crasta, Carol Sequeira &amp; upcoming talented singer Miss Karen Crasta, this album will take the listener on a musical ride!\n\nMusic composed and arranged by Roshan Dsouza angelore, a maestro and a stalwart of Konkani music, a music director par excellence. Mixed and mastered by Nithin K, Orpheus Studio- Ernakulam. Lyrics are written by Lloyd Rego, Wilson Kateel and Sanjay Borkar. Songs have been recorded at Sandesha Studio (Mangalore), Studio 5 (Mangalore) and AudioKraft Studio, Kuwait.', 'Mi Amor by Orson D''souza', '<em>Mi Amor</em>is Orson Dsouzas debut Konkani music album. Better known as Awesome Orson, he was the winner of Gulf Voice of Mangalore Season 3.<em>Mi Amor</em>was released on 23rd November.\n\n<strong>Physical copies (CD format) will be available within India at Rs. 150 (inclusive of shipping cost).</strong>\n\n<strong>Music lovers worldwide can buy downloadable MP3 album at Rs. 250.</strong>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '221-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-11-21 14:48:11', '2018-11-21 09:18:11', '', 221, 'https://store.paypassion.in/2018/10/31/221-autosave-v1/', 0, 'r