(380, 1, '2018-11-04 10:29:31', '2018-11-04 04:59:31', '[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qDIQfjYswbc[/embed]\r\n\r\nJinye Rangg- Colurs of Life\r\nKonkani Music CD\r\n\r\nJinye Rangg is the maiden Konkani Music album by well-known writer and poet Walter Dantis.\r\nThe songs in this unique music CD are chosen from his popular Poetry book  nidon Podllo gaanv ( "The sleeping village" ). Walter who has written lyrics for the popular Konkani hits like  vengenth dharum,  kirak mog peracho ,  Saandun gellya cheduva etc.\r\n\r\nHe is teamed up with a young and talented music director, composer Loy Valentine Saldanha who has been trained at AR Rehman Institute and has composed Music for several short films, TV serials and Music albums.\r\n\r\nThe album contains voices of some of the best known singers in the Konkani music industry and some young talents. Nihal Tauro , Robin sequiera, Ashwin Dcosta, Velita Lobo, Laveena Dantis, Munita veigas, Akshada, Melwyn Antony Dsouza, Sachin Saldanha, Loy Saldanha and introducing young talent Ashna DSilva.\r\n\r\nThe Live instruments support for this CD have been given by Alston Gomes (Saxophone, Clarinet &amp; Brass) Ruben Machado ( Flute) ,Patson Periera ( Guitar), Sunil Kumar( Violin) Disha Pasanna( backing Vocals).', '  by Walter Dantis', 'Jinye Rangg Konkani Music Album by Walter Dantis.\r\n\r\nLyrics by Walter Dantis.\r\nTunes, Music and Arrangements by Loy Valentine Saldanha.\r\n\r\nDelivery only within India.\r\nDownloadable format for International buyers!', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'jinnye-rangg-by-walter-dantis', '', '', '2018-11-23 12:10:28', '2018-11-23 06:40:28', '', 0, 'https://store.paypassion.in/?post_type=product&#038;p=380', 0, 'product', '', 0),
